Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔馳的馬蹄聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過那平緩的丘陵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向這裡奔馳的馬車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來迎接我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來迎接我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會有一個人來把我帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往開滿白花的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往風的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會帶走我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會帶走我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“被神召喚”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊天氣真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生我現在要去一下工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬丁啊不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便到郵局去一趟幫我帶份報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個好幫手幫了我不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你更應該要休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天的氣候還滿穩定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯收成應該不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該再休息一下才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該去把犛具整理一下才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是因為安妮在家工作特別起勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心喔馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他又跟一樣有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一件也洗洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬修的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又是心臟病發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮快點去找馬丁來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在穀倉那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬丁快來幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去找史賓塞醫生過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便請林德太太過來幫忙你聽到了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點啊馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼馬修病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要駕馬車趕快去請醫生來所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了你趕快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就會恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林德夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次大概不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道馬修他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看馬修的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這麼多次看他發病的情形看來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮看著他的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得他好像只是睡著似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當醫生來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只能宣佈馬修已經過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他沒有經過什麼死前的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為受到某種驚嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後來才知道他受到驚嚇的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是握在手中的那一份報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比銀行倒閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修一定是看到這個受了刺激…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉我早就說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比銀行有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們當初聽我的勸告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會…林德夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮妳說得一點都沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人死不能復生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道現在說這個可能不太恰當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳一定要節哀順變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為眼前妳還有很多事情要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會了解的對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉妳怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道妳的感受可是妳一定要振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉現在的情緒很不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要打起精神來幫助她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬丁你去貝瑞家通知一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要告訴貝爾先生知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須打電報通知卡伯特家的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知不知道怎麼連絡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果貝爾先生跟其他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠快一點到這兒來很多事就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想服喪的標示應該掛到門口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉的母親過世的時候應該有留下來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之妳們該振作起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修卡伯特過世的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快的就傳遍了愛蒙利亞這個小地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一天之內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生前的朋友鄰居都來到了綠色莊園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來見馬修的遺容並對遺族致上無限的哀悼之意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會發生這麼出人意外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要幫忙要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳戴安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮 棺木已經送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一雙馬修穿的白襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一條羊毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫往生者擦拭身體的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有的話棉的也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一次也是最後一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞內向的馬修卡伯特成了眾人注意的焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修平日使用的煙斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也特別放在馬修的手中陪伴著他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮離開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人悄悄的來到花園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些看起來很素雅的花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬修和瑪麗拉的媽媽那一代就開始種植的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個花圃也是馬修一直很用心在默默耕種的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮慘白的臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一雙流不出淚的感傷眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一朵一朵小心翼翼的摘下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把花獻給馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是安妮最後一次能幫馬修所做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然終有到達的一天主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅程結束前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日落也隨之將盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依石就寢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在假寐的夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也受到上帝的守護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修你真是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起我可以進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天晚上來這裡陪妳一起睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人陪妳睡會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳戴安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳能諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在想要一個人單獨的靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情發生之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有一個人獨處過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想自己一個人靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在還是無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一半的時問我相信馬修並沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好像已經過了很久很久似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒有像這樣被這種心痛的感覺迷惑過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉戴安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴安娜並不了解安妮說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉看起來很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情就像狂風暴雨一般的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她帶來莫大的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮為什麼一滴眼淚都沒有流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個人忍著傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓安妮去整理她雜亂的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的戴安娜什麼話也沒說就靜靜的離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個令人悲傷的夜晚安妮選擇一個人度過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當安妮一個人獨處時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想為這個疼愛自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情都替自己設想的馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的痛哭一場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是竟然連一滴眼淚也流不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太沒有道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一天才跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夕陽裡散步的馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻穿著整齊臉色慘白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人靜靜的躺在棺木裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她還是沒有流下眼淚來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的只是那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:18:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的感覺和說不出來的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮她靜靜的一個人跪在窗前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一打的男孩子唷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子一定沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到艾凡瑞獎學金的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要女孩子才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我的乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是讓我感到騎傲的乖孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮是我的乖女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再哭馬修也不會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼勸妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我自己也沒辦法克制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修是我唯一的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一個這麼善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只有上帝最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我哭瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然淚水不能讓我好過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳留下來瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能夠讓戴安娜留下來陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她對我真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這不是她的痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴安娜她沒有辦法真正體會我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉這是妳跟我的傷痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了馬修之後我們該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該彼此關心好好的過下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮如果妳不在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有妳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道現在的我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮我知道有時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對妳太嚴苛了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳不要認為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不像馬修那樣疼愛妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把心裡話說出來不是件容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了像現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道我要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對妳就像是對自己親生骨肉那樣的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從妳來到綠色莊園之後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.10,0:23:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才知道什麼叫幸福快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗拉安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回清秀佳人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“永別了馬修”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請按時觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.37,0:24:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直向前跑著向前跑著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.51,0:24:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿波浪般開滿的花
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然不見盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖在很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲在更遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.53,0:24:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在花叢中渡過一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.37,0:25:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是一個未醒的夢般
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是一個未醒的夢般
